    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies PT-TLS, a TLS-based Posture Transport (PT) protocol.  The PT-TLS protocol carries the Network Endpoint Assessment (NEA) message exchange under the protection of a Transport Layer Security (TLS) secured tunnel.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
